\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
e^{-\varepsilon n}\leq\delta\iff-\varepsilon n\leq\ln\left(\delta\right)\iff n\geq\frac{1}{\varepsilon}\ln\left(\frac{1}{\delta}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

